comment.body:
@Alex-302 The new filtering rule "ntdeals.net##div[class^="ads-game-page-"]" does not filter the ads in the main page, which are div "ads-games-collection" - https://ntdeals.net/us-store/discounts

The suggested rule that was done for their other site (XBDeals) works great for this. Can you please update the filtering rule to ntdeals.net##div[class^="ads-game"]

Thank you!

